ğŸ›¡ï¸ Trust & Security Section
Security, Compliance & Trust Framework

NatioID is designed around global digital-identity and public-infrastructure standards:

Pillar	Standards / Approach
Digital Identity Foundation	NIST Digital Identity Guidelines, W3C Verifiable Credentials
Security Architecture	Zero-Trust, Multi-level Identity Verification, Secure Signing
Encryption	End-to-End Encryption, Encrypted Storage, TLS Everywhere
Data Governance	GDPR-aligned privacy principles, audit logs, role-based access
Election Integrity	Verifiable logs, traceability, anti-tamper logic design
Fraud Prevention	Identity binding, device trust checks, misuse detection flags

Built to support sovereign identity, citizen privacy, and electoral transparency.

